  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as River as they have a trip over the weekend with their friends. Choose what River does during the trip. Will they hang out with their friends? Will they explore the cabin? Or will they choose to just let the trip pass by as quickly as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744450/extras/6311f30cb18ed9059168d796489cc4f8.avif?t=1754296470\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- point-and-click gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- choose how River talks to their friends</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- choose how River reacts to their surroundings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- simple puzzles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- hand drawn sprites and backgrounds</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- atmospheric and ambient music</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744450/extras/2ac7f8cadb65dc4e18101bc8442dd31b.avif?t=1754296470\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
